{"tid":2254875,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"反送中文物展 以敍事延續抗爭","createTime":"2020-10-23T06:49:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-23T06:49:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b92a9dccf251325bb39863cc8868171ee9fb45cc","tid":2254875,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T06:49:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201023/5YTZEGJOXNH7JNILL7NPH6CTXY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201023%2F5YTZEGJOXNH7JNILL7NPH6CTXY%2F&d=LL0CSI02xgrrxVkOh%2Fu%2FRHG%2F0kAjhv1dd93UXbk31gU%3D&h=8d9ca2ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201023%2F5YTZEGJOXNH7JNILL7NPH6CTXY%2F&h=6747cdc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201023/5YTZEGJOXNH7JNILL7NPH6CTXY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n反送中文物展 以敍事延續抗爭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5-nKj4pH1xchnvKTuMkFbFprt7g=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IYMSUTQPOFE4TKBQBB46Y3YLI4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5-nKj4pH1xchnvKTuMkFbFprt7g%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIYMSUTQPOFE4TKBQBB46Y3YLI4.jpg&h=9a379068&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■物敍創辦人Stary希望藉展覽讓大眾憶起反修例期間發生的一切。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一件平常不過的物件，背後卻承載不少人的盼望，黃色雨傘、連儂牆等令港人聯想起過去近一年半反修例運動中的點滴。「物敍｜Objournalist」一連兩星期在香港大學舉辦「格物：反修例運動文物展」，展出他們在運動期間所收集的物件，盼藉物件讓大眾反思自己在抗爭活動中的定位，透過以物敍事方式延續抗爭活動。<br />\n<br />\n展覽一共展出了15件物件，包括一把寫有「光時」口號的黃色雨傘及黃店收據，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現場收集物品 記錄歷史<br />\n<br />\n創辦人Stary表示，希望藉物件的實在感，讓大眾憶起反修例期間發生的一切，「物件就係物件，好難話改寫物件，因為呢個係歷史證據。」負責人Offy 更形容文物展猶如港版「戰爭博物館」。<br />\n<br />\n15件物件中最引人注目的是一把黃色雨傘。Stary指該雨傘來自7.21元朗站事件一周年活動，由一位女士捐贈，「當時市面上已經幾乎冇黃遮賣，加上把遮印咗光時口號，令到成件物件更加有價值。」但口號增添團隊籌備文物展時的壓力，最終經商量後決定只展示「命」一字。<br />\n<br />\n文物展亦展出一批台式飲品店收據，每張收據上寫有不同的抗爭口號，由「香港加油」、「香港人反抗」到「香港人報仇」。Stary指收據「本身有五蚊銀咁，我嗰陣就好似考古咁，一層層將收據揭開。」<br />\n<br />\n文物展中最令人印象深刻的是港鐵單程車票，配以8.31太子站事件片段的錄音，不禁令人想起當日警暴的畫面。Stary慨嘆，「香港人好似遺忘咗啲嘢&hellip;&hellip;由黨鐵變返做港鐵，仲開始搭返」。<br />\n<br />\n團體表示，今次文物展是首次在港舉辦，正積極物色其他展覽場地，亦希望收集更多與運動有關的物件，傳承每件物件的故事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/mWaqRtn_j8JhPpaVbAAEqyVfc3c=/1644x665/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NXHOPTROQ5G3BJIGP34SV6O5JE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FmWaqRtn_j8JhPpaVbAAEqyVfc3c%3D%2F1644x665%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNXHOPTROQ5G3BJIGP34SV6O5JE.jpg&h=b4008fb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/m3l5XQfoClOUAmrc-cf7yJFgRXM=/919x624/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/F4TTW5V6CNEX7BBEIHWDODRDUY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fm3l5XQfoClOUAmrc-cf7yJFgRXM%3D%2F919x624%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FF4TTW5V6CNEX7BBEIHWDODRDUY.jpg&h=1ede58ad&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}